<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>Nexus - Agentic AI Framework</title>
        <link
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap"
            rel="stylesheet"
        />
        <link
            href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css"
            rel="stylesheet"
        />
        <style>
            :root {
                --primary-color: #1a237e;
                --secondary-color: #6efff5;
            }
            body {
                font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #333;
                background: #f0f2f5;
            }
            .bg-primary {
                background-color: var(--primary-color);
            }
            .bg-secondary {
                background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            }
            .text-primary {
                color: var(--primary-color);
            }
            .text-secondary {
                color: var(--secondary-color);
            }
            .border-primary {
                border-color: var(--primary-color);
            }
            .border-secondary {
                border-color: var(--secondary-color);
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
        <header class="bg-primary text-white p-4 fixed w-full z-10">
            <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Nexus</h1>
                <nav>
                    <ul class="flex space-x-4">
                        <li>
                            <a href="#features" class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors"
                                >Features</a
                            >
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a href="#design" class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors"
                                >Design</a
                            >
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            <a href="/login" class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors"
                                >Login</a
                            >
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a href="/register" class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors"
                                >Register</a
                            >
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main class="flex-grow">
            <section
                class="hero bg-cover bg-center h-screen flex items-center relative"
                style="background-image: url('/AI.png')"
            >
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-60"></div>
                <div class="container mx-auto text-center relative z-1 text-white">
                    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Nexus: Agentic AI Framework</h1>
                    <p class="text-xl mb-8">
                        Revolutionize complex task solving with advanced AI collaboration and
                        seamless tool integration
                    </p>
                    <a
                        href="/app"
                        class="bg-secondary text-primary px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-colors"
                        >Get Started</a
                    >
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="features" class="py-20 bg-white">
                <div class="container mx-auto">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-primary">Key Features</h2>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                        <div class="feature p-6 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">
                                Multi-agent Collaboration
                            </h3>
                            <p>
                                Harness the collective intelligence of multiple AI agents working in
                                harmony to tackle complex challenges.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature p-6 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">
                                Dynamic Tool Selection
                            </h3>
                            <p>
                                Automatically identify and deploy the most effective tools for each
                                unique task, optimizing efficiency and results.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature p-6 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">
                                External API Integration
                            </h3>
                            <p>
                                Seamlessly connect with a wide array of external services and data
                                sources to enhance capabilities and insights.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature p-6 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">
                                Task Decomposition
                            </h3>
                            <p>
                                Break down complex tasks into manageable subtasks for efficient
                                processing and parallel execution.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature p-6 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">
                                Adaptive Learning
                            </h3>
                            <p>
                                Continuously evolve and refine performance through experience,
                                feedback, and cutting-edge machine learning techniques.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature p-6 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">
                                Real-time Decision Making
                            </h3>
                            <p>
                                Make informed decisions on-the-fly using real-time data analysis and
                                predictive modeling.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="design" class="py-20 bg-gray-100">
                <div class="container mx-auto">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-primary">
                        Design Considerations
                    </h2>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                        <div class="design-card p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">AI Models</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
                                <li>Multiple AI provider integration</li>
                                <li>Model pairing for optimal performance</li>
                                <li>Meta-learning for quick adaptation</li>
                                <li>Federated learning for privacy</li>
                                <li>Fine-tuning for specific tasks</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="design-card p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">
                                Tool Integration
                            </h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
                                <li>Standardized interface for tools</li>
                                <li>Automatic tool discovery</li>
                                <li>Version control for configurations</li>
                                <li>A/B testing for tool performance</li>
                                <li>Plugin system for new tools</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="design-card p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">
                                Security and Privacy
                            </h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
                                <li>Role-based access control</li>
                                <li>Audit logging for all actions</li>
                                <li>Compliance with data protection regulations</li>
                                <li>Secure API key handling</li>
                                <li>End-to-end encryption</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <footer class="bg-primary text-white py-8">
            <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
                <p>&copy; 2024 Nexus. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </body>
</html>
